      "role": "user",
      "content": "wow spreading to the brain?? that sounds kinda scary lol. i dont really have time to go to a clinic today though, i have a huge deadline. can i just try some of those redness relief drops like Visine or something to see if it clears up for a bit? i really need to get through this work day.",
